lead_paragraph: Manchester City failed to win for a fifth successive game in all competitions on Sunday, only avoiding a loss to Southampton when Kelechi Iheanacho produced a second-half equalizer for a 1-1 draw.

headline.print_headline: Man City Winless Run Reaches 5 Games With Southampton Draw
headline.main: Man City Winless Run Reaches 5 Games With Southampton Draw
